Mouse problems
\""""""""""""""
 "My mouse does not work in Avalot, but it does work
   in Windows. Why?"

To use your mouse in Avalot, you need to have a DOS
mouse driver installed. You should have received one
with your mouse, together with installation
instructions.

Your mouse works in Windows, because Windows uses its
own mouse drivers.
